MODULE
     asn1rt - ASN.1 runtime support functions

DESCRIPTION
     This module is the interface module for  the  ASN.1  runtime
     support  functions. To encode and decode ASN.1 types in run-
     time the functions in this module should be used.


EXPORTS
     encode(Module,{Type,Value})-> {ok,Bytes}| {error,Reason}
     encode(Module,Type,Value)-> {ok,Bytes} | {error,Reason}

          Types
               Module = Type = atom()
               Value = term()
               Bytes = [Int] when integer(Int), Int >= 0, Int  =<
               255
               Reason = term()

